<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>.. دَرْكِ الأُصُولِ مَعَ الْفُرُوعِ وَذَانِ<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>أَبَدًا إِلَيْهِ حُكْمَهَا لا غَيْرُهُ<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>فَالْحُكْمُ مَا حَكَمَتْ بِهِ النَّصَانِ<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span>يَا هِجْرَةً طَالَتْ مَسَافَتُهَا عَلَى<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span>مَنْ خَصَّ بِالْحُرْمَانِ وَالْخُذْلانِ<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span>يَا هِجْرَةً طَالَتْ مَسَافَتُهَا عَلَى<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span>كَسْلان مَنْخُوبِ الْفُؤَادِ جَبَانِ<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span>يَا هِجْرَةً وَالْعَبْدُ فَوْقَ فِرَاشِهِ<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span>سَبَقَ السُّعَاةَ لِمَنْزِلِ الرِّضْوَانِ<a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span>سَارُوا أَحَثَّ السَّيْرِ وَهُوَ فَسَيْرُهُ<a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p11"></span>سَيْرُ الدَّلالِ وَلَيْسَ بِالذَّمِلانِ<a href="#p11" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p12"></span>هَذَا وَتَنْظُرُه أَمَامَ الرَّكْبِ كَالْـ<a href="#p12" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p13"></span>ـعِلْمِ الْعَظِيمِ يُشَافُ فِي الْقِيعَانِ<a href="#p13" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p14"></span>رُفِعَتْ لَهُ أَعْلامُ هَاتِيكَ النُّصُو<a href="#p14" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p15"></span>صِ رُؤُوسُهَا شَابَتْ مِنَ النِّيرَانِ<a href="#p15" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p16"></span>نَارٌ هِيَ النُّورُ الْمُبِينُ وَلَمْ يَكُنْ<a href="#p16" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p17"></span>لِيَرَاهُ إِلا مَنْ لَهُ عَيْنَانِ<a href="#p17" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p18"></span>مَكْحُولَتَانِ بِمِرْوَدِ الْوَحْيَيْنِ لا<a href="#p18" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p19"></span>بِمَرَاوُدِ الآرَاءِ وَالْهَذَياَنِ<a href="#p19" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p20"></span>فَلِذَاكِ شَمَّرَ نَحْوَهَا لَمْ يَلْتَفِتْ<a href="#p20" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p21"></span>لا عَنْ شَمَائِلِهِ وَلا أَيْمَانِ<a href="#p21" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>